      • compareRows

        public int compareRows(Cell left,
                       Cell right)
        从类复制的说明: CellComparatorImpl
        Compares the rows of the left and right cell. For the hbase:meta case this method is overridden such that it can handle hbase:meta cells. The caller should ensure using the appropriate comparator for hbase:meta.
        指定者:
        compareRows 在接口中 CellComparator
        覆盖:
        compareRows 在类中 CellComparatorImpl
        参数:
        left - the left hand side cell
        right - the right hand side cell
        返回:
        0 if both cells are equal, 1 if left cell is bigger than right, -1 otherwise

      • compareRows

        public int compareRows(Cell left,
                       byte[] right,
                       int roffset,
                       int rlength)
        从类复制的说明: CellComparatorImpl
        Compares the row part of the cell with a simple plain byte[] like the stopRow in Scan. This should be used with context where for hbase:meta cells the {CellComparatorImpl.META_COMPARATOR should be used
        指定者:
        compareRows 在接口中 CellComparator
        覆盖:
        compareRows 在类中 CellComparatorImpl
        参数:
        left - the cell to be compared
        right - the kv serialized byte[] to be compared with
        roffset - the offset in the byte[]
        rlength - the length in the byte[]
        返回:
        0 if both cell and the byte[] are equal, 1 if the cell is bigger than byte[], -1 otherwise

      • compare

        public int compare(Cell a,
                   Cell b,
                   boolean ignoreSequenceid)
        从接口复制的说明: CellComparator
        Compare cells.
        指定者:
        compare 在接口中 CellComparator
        覆盖:
        compare 在类中 CellComparatorImpl
        ignoreSequenceid - True if we are to compare the key portion only and ignore the sequenceid. Set to false to compare key and consider sequenceid.
        返回:
        0 if equal, -1 if a < b, and +1 if a > b.

      • getSimpleComparator

        public Comparator getSimpleComparator()
        指定者:
        getSimpleComparator 在接口中 CellComparator
        覆盖:
        getSimpleComparator 在类中 CellComparatorImpl
        返回:
        A dumbed-down, fast comparator for hbase2 base-type, the ByteBufferKeyValue. Create an instance when you make a new memstore, when you know only BBKVs will be passed. Do not pollute with types other than BBKV if can be helped; the Comparator will slow.
